Project: Market Data Feed Handler (Streaming Engine)
    This is VERY relevant to trading firms
    They process live market data streams continuously

What You Will Build
    A system that:
        Reads tick-by-tick market data
        Processes it in real-time
        Calculates:
            Last price
            Moving average
            Price updates

Concepts You Will Learn
    File streaming (like real-time feed)
    Efficient data handling
    Sliding window (important in trading)
    Clean architecture

Why This Project Matters
This shows:
    You understand data streaming (core in trading)
    You can handle continuous input
    You apply efficient algorithms (sliding window)

This is directly relevant to market data systems

Next Upgrades (IMPORTANT)
    Turn this into a strong project:
    Level 2:
        Add multi-symbol support (map)
        Store latest price per symbol
    Level 3:
        Add multi-threading
            Thread 1 → read data
            Thread 2 → process data
    Level 4:
        Replace file with TCP socket feed